title: Best of The Program | Guests: Jason Buttrill & Dr. Karlyn Borysenko | 7/28/20
description:
Globalism is coming, whether we like it or not, as the World Economic Forum sets up a “Great Reset.” Jason Buttrill joins to talk more about the Forum’s plan to form public-private partnerships, modify capitalism, and digitize everything. Dr. Karlyn Borysenko breaks down why there’s such a big political divide over masks. Attorney General Barr is set to testify today to the House Judiciary Committee as Democrats look to impeach him, but Fox News’ coverage is mysteriously missing from Google’s top search results.
